  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a hot pot vessel over medium heat. Add onion and garlic, cook until softened.",
    "Add caraway seeds and bay leaves, cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add tomato paste, cook for 1 minute, stirring constantly.",
    "Add white wine and vegetable broth, bring to a simmer.",
    "Add borlotti beans, salt, and black pepper, stir to combine.",
    "Cover the pot with a papillote, transfer to a preheated oven at 180°C.",
    "Bake for 25 minutes, or until the beans are tender.",
    "Remove from oven, let cool slightly before serving."
